READ.ME 2022-01-05
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is a fully configured maven build and spring boot application with AngularJS for testing purposes.

This app containing a word wrapping service for demo reasons. It is a concurrent threading implementation.

Test webapp is included. Run the SpringBootWrappingServiceRESTAngularJS app as java app in your favorite IDE.
Test is possible at url http://localhost:8080/textWrapAngularJS.html.

Webapp form:
Enter -1 for new request (default) or enter returned workId for existing requests.

Single way tested, not tested on big loads.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Update 2022-01-17

if git and maven is locally installed, do following steps to run the project
git clone -b master https://github.com/profgvamosi/SpringBootWrappingServiceRESTAngularJS.git
mvn spring-boot:run -Dapp.profiles=test

JUnit 4 Mockito test added.

